# React / UI

- Functional components; explicit prop `type`s.
- Feature code lives in `src/features/<feature>/`.
- Shared layout/primitives in `src/components/`.
- Global styles in `src/styles/`; avoid inline styles unless dynamic.
- Canvas nodes: add under `src/features/canvas/nodes/` and register `nodeTypes` on React Flow.
